{"tid":984839,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"寫詩罵同學「渣男」 一名台灣男大學生遭侮辱罪嫌起訴","createTime":"2019-01-17T06:17:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T14:28:12.000Z","uid":100680,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fd74476ccf95d8150c25e07a362c98590a8c8227","tid":984839,"uid":100680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T06:17:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/01/08/realtime/5766345.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F01%2F08%2Frealtime%2F5766345.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=baf4e29c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n施姓、彭姓男大生因故對廖姓同學不滿，前年11月間由彭構思了1首「藏頭詩」，每一句話開頭唸起來就是指廖是渣男，並由施將這首詩PO上網路論壇DCARD，後來廖輾轉發現，因為不甘辱報警提告，檢方認為，施發文指摘廖為「渣男」犯嫌明確，偵結依公然侮辱罪嫌起訴施。<br />\n<br />\n檢警調查，施、彭及廖3人都是同一所大學同學，但施、彭因為細故和廖不睦，就由施構思寫了一首藏頭詩，再傳Line請施PO上DCARD論壇並以「絕對爆卦 大二最渣來報到」標題，內容除了指摘廖認識很多女生，是否太過囂張，每一句的開頭唸起來就是廖的本名是「渣男」。<br />\n<br />\n廖看見後認為對方指名道姓，而且該貼文是不特定多數人都可以看見，認為自己人格、社會評價受損，對施提告加重誹謗。<br />\n<br />\n施到案坦承有用自己帳號在論壇發文，並用藏頭詩方式暗諷廖男是渣男，但否認有妨害名譽犯行，而廖指證歷歷，也有網路截圖文字內容等，檢方偵結依公然侮辱罪嫌將施男起訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7321/3580961\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7321%2F3580961&d=c8V27Lgsxe1lABVcT2XcUKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=d7d178fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7321/3580961</a>"},{"pid":"26c018a74ba6840e1537f0c737ee2f7973506984","tid":984839,"uid":12449,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T06:22:36.000Z","msg":"小學雞讀大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bfa200596cf5c75c96a76e42f717be3896b951b","tid":984839,"uid":152370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T06:37:49.000Z","msg":"陳庭佳有埋片都未出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8ff0ee77bdc335b6f13a57c77f28e2983724bfa","tid":984839,"uid":100680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T14:28:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}